00:21:07.684 --> 00:21:10.062
Angelo, izaberi si ženu.

00:21:10.938 --> 00:21:12.731
Mama, nemam više 13 godina.

00:21:13.023 --> 00:21:14.149
Maria, Costa?

00:21:14.441 --> 00:21:16.193
Pridružila nam se nova obitelj.

00:21:16.443 --> 00:21:18.153
Bok.
